%% Diagram: Inline cache state lifecycle — uninitialized to mono, poly, megamorphic with access cost and TurboFan implication
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TB
    U["Uninitialized<br/>0 shapes<br/>no feedback"]
    M["Monomorphic<br/>1 shape<br/>~3 cycles<br/>TurboFan: aggressive specialization"]
    P["Polymorphic<br/>2 to 4 shapes<br/>~10 to 20 cycles<br/>TurboFan: limited specialization"]
    G["Megamorphic<br/>more than 4 shapes<br/>~100+ cycles, global stub cache<br/>TurboFan: typically refuses"]

    U -->|"first shape observed"| M
    M -->|"second different shape"| P
    P -->|"shapes 3 and 4"| P
    P -->|"shape 5 or more"| G
    G -->|"any further shape"| G

    style U fill:#e3f2fd
    style M fill:#e8f5e8
    style P fill:#fff3e0
    style G fill:#ffebee
